{"about_the_game":"<strong>Void Destroyer - Mini Sandbox</strong> is a proof of concept - of the planned sequel to Void Destroyer - released for fans to enjoy, give feedback and generate ideas.<br><br>While the &quot;mini sandbox&quot; has a lot of common sandbox features - it lacks the intended depth/polish of a full release and many planned features of Void Destroyer 2.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">For these and other reasons this DLC is free to owners of Void Destroyer.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Start with a small fighter - work your way up in the universe<br></li><li> Expand your fleet with wingmen<br></li><li> Complete missions for factions<br></li><li> Collect bounties on pirates<br></li><li> Purchase resources for trade - or steal them from cargo ships<br></li><li> Persistent and living (though minimal) open sandbox<br></li><li> Estimated 5 hours of play time</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">I hope you enjoy getting a sneak peek at a sandbox experience in the Void Destroyer universe.</h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363320/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1447372653","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363320/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1447372653","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363320/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1447372653","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363320/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1447372653","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Downloadable Content","id":21},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<strong>Void Destroyer - Mini Sandbox</strong> is a proof of concept - of the planned sequel to Void Destroyer - released for fans to enjoy, give feedback and generate ideas.<br><br>While the